    "description": {
      "zh": "1P69“Hyperon”变倍瞄准镜是“Hyperon”瞄准镜的改进版，为在SV-98上安装准备，以提高战场上的效能。该瞄准镜具有灵活的调焦倍数，以及相当精确的测距仪，方便组合运算，可测量到目标的距离并输入瞄准角度。",
      "en": "The 1P69 \"Giperon\" pancratic sight is a further development of the \"Giperon\" sights and is intended for installation on the SV-98 sniper rifle in order to increase the effectiveness on the battlefield. The sight has a flexible adjustment multiples, as well as a fairly accurate range finder, facilitating the operation of combining, measuring the distance to the target and entering the aiming angles."
    },
